author: Erica Hernandez
title: Star Wars to premiere #TheForceAwakens trailer during Monday...
text:
Star Wars announced Sunday that it will release the full trailer to its latest movie franchise installment, 'The Force Awakens,' tonight during Monday Night Football. After the trailer debuts on Monday, fans will immediately be able to buy tickets to the movie that hits theaters on Dec. 18.
